{"tid":1246921,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"我係現場，我建議重啟佔領中環！（解夢）","createTime":"2019-06-21T02:33:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-21T03:00:28.000Z","uid":32191,"like":4,"dislike":22,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"f0f3144aa9e5744f6ee41daee3536ab19a82a8bb","tid":1246921,"uid":32191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T02:33:22.000Z","msg":"發夢夢到以下內容：<br />\n講真依加坐立會包圍立會根本無用，<br />\n其實果時啲學者中環個plan 真心work，<br />\n點解大家唔試吓？<br />\n<br />\n依加現場啲人討論得幾個plan，<br />\nPlan A 包立會 (極消耗！無目標！政府無壓力）下下策<br />\nPlan B 包狗總 (有目標！政府有壓力！但送硬頭）下策<br />\nPlan C 包禮賓府（有目標！有壓力！但已有防備）可行方案<br />\n<br />\n我建議佔中！<br />\n原因一，可以和平唔洗送頭，捉咗罪名俾暴動罪低<br />\n原因二，直擊香港精英國際之地，俾全世界都睇到<br />\n原因三，旅遊經濟重地，直接影響香港<br />\n原因四，地點多補合位攻防位，可以長期作戰<br />\n原因五，新鮮感，行動要有新方向，香港人就係咁，要有新鮮感先會有新一輪抗爭<br />\n原因六，中環未有防備！依加進攻一流！<br />\n<br />\n大家幫手推推多啲人入嚟傾吓依個夢！"},{"pid":"f8acd4b5a0020011100b00f2925fb2cb8a727e83","tid":1246921,"uid":122676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T02:34:03.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8a1ba0e21300dbafc8396b091d3550094f75a882","tid":1246921,"uid":32191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T02:34:44.000Z","msg":"推一推，個夢夢見現場好多人好攰好消耗，快啲傾"},{"pid":"56f0ddcd5e085039e06f78453ed73b5baedec8b3","tid":1246921,"uid":2612,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T02:36:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>今次肯定得：我岩岩po左信上美國大媒體Buzzfeed，麻煩入link留comment同share去！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.buzzfeed.com/hongkongkidsaredying/hong-kong-citizens-need-your-help-emf7dtv2y2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.buzzfeed.com%2Fhongkongkidsaredying%2Fhong-kong-citizens-need-your-help-emf7dtv2y2&d=pb8keE2dQvveSnD3H4ranlpzQI%2FFghXCkDWT3grjsfs%3D&h=f8e2d35c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.buzzfeed.com/hongkongkidsaredying/hong-kong-citizens-need-your-help-emf7dtv2y2</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我個新post（請順便幫我推，我第三晚通頂，跪求可憐我）<